text: Tobias Hildebrand (born 20 October 1975) is a retired Swedish tennis player. Hildebrand has a career high ATP singles ranking of 427 achieved on 29 September 1997. He also has a career high doubles ranking of 210 achieved on 5 July 1999. Hildebrand has won 2 ATP Challenger doubles titles at the 1998 Tampere Open and the 1998 Scheveningen Challenger. ==Tour titles== {| class=wikitable !
